Book wiki mission statement 0.1:
  The goal of book wiki is to enable authors to easily create and navigate complex worlds by creating an easy to
  navigate system that stores both the story and worlds in one place.

MVP Goals:
  Many users can create many books with many chapters that have many elements.
  chapters have the ability to link elements inside of text
    ex. we reference Joffery Smoshfery, you can highlight him in the chapter and go to the element
  

Domain definition:
  book:
    a collection of chapters that follow a story
  chapter:
    a piece of text that contains content
  elements:
    pieces of a story, can be a character/location/event